Add a New Project
=================

#. Click the <i class="fa fa-bars"></i> **menu icon** in the ribbon
#. Click **Finance**
#. Click **Projects**
#. Click the <i class="fa fa-plus"></i> **plus icon** in the upper right hand corner
#. Enter a project title
#. Choose a type
#. Enter a program code
#. Enter a source code
#. Enter a match
#. Enter a main project code
#. Enter a country project code
#. Click **Save**
#. If desired, `export </users/finance/guides/export_records.html>`_ project data
#. If desired, `edit <users/finance/guides/how_to_edit.html>`_ projects
#. If desired, `merge </users/finance/guides/how_to_merge.html>`_ projects
